summary: I kinda want Retsuko to SLOWLY fall for Haida and not even realize it.  Like, she doesn't even recognize it as 'love', but that...
body:
I kinda want Retsuko to SLOWLY fall for Haida and not even realize it. Like, she doesn’t even recognize it as ‘love’, but that the more they hang out together, the more she enjoys it and the more she wants to spend time with him.

Then something happens like Haida gets a special project that puts him out of the office for a while. Or, though it’s a bit cliche, he’s assigned to work with another coworker on a project and starts spending more time on that and….it’s not so much that Retsuko gets jealous as it is that she misses Haida’s presence and kinda wonders if the other coworker, who seems to get along well with Haida, sees in him what it’s taken Retsuko so long to see…or she’s worried that she’ll 'lose’ him, basically.

And Haida, it’s kinda not even on his radar because he’s resigned himself to the idea Retsuko may never like him the way he likes her, and he’s been happy to just spend more time with her.

And like, it’s not until one night when he’s working REALLY late, like maybe later than Ton usually had Retsuko, and she’s outside waiting for him. And, obviously worried about HER well-being, he’s like, “Wh-what are you still doing here? I thought you went home already?”

….

And there’s a beat.

And Retsuko kinda realizes how ridiculous it was for her to stay that late, and she’s a bit embarrassed, but she quietly says, “I guess… I just really missed you.”

And Haida’s eyes kinda get wide and his heart flutters because he realizes it’s the closest sign he has that Retsuko may be starting to feel the same way he does, because he always really misses her when he’s away from her for too long too.

❤

And it doesn’t mean they start dating quite yet, but they’re closer and it’s not far off.

💕 And Haida realizes he actually may have a chance! 💕 😊

summary: Quick little update for everyone! As you may see...the Christmas story isn’t here yet. For the record, I HAVE been working on...
body:
Quick little update for everyone! As you may see…the Christmas story isn’t here yet. For the record, I HAVE been working on it. Even going through life ‘n shit, it’s still coming. But there IS a reason why it’s taking a little bit longer.

As much as I make jokes saying that the Christmas special totally traumatized me, like some kinda ‘Nam flashback, the truth is it actually has been quite impactful, in regards to the writing for the story. Prior to it coming out, I had really only a rough idea for where I wanted the story to go, but after seeing it, a bigger idea began to take shape. Suddenly, the story took on a different idea, and now it’s rather different from my original idea (to where I decided to change the name….well, rather, I expanded the name, to match the two ideas being sandwiched in) Hopefully, people will like it, and it kinda fills the hole in the hearts that the special’s ending was only able to fill so much of. :)

As I’m writing this, I have the document up right now, and it’s about…..80-85% done, I wanna say? And I just got some free time, so I should be able to crank it out by tonight. Though, depending on how life goes again, I may end up having to upload it tomorrow, Christmas eve.

which is actually funny considering what happens in the story and when it takes place LMAOOOOOOO

summary: What are some shows you like to watch?
question: What are some shows you like to watch?
answer:
Hi Anon! Well I am more of a movie kind of person but I do watch some shows just to kill time but I don’t really get into them that much. The only shows that I am really invested are:

Ducktales 2017. This one is my favorite 💕 I haven’t seen the original and when YouTube recommended me the first episode I had nothing else to do at that moment so I decided to watch it to kill some time. I never expected to LOVE this show so much 😍 but I blame Huey, Dewey, Louie and Webby, these kids are wonderful and I love how well they play off each other, if it wasn’t for them I wouldn’t be so into this.

This one is pretty short but it’s cute and funny 😆 I love Retsuko and how she can change from demure girl to loud metal-loving girl. I also like the side characters Haida and Fenecko and I totally ship RetsukoxHaida 😍

Actually I never knew about Miraculous Ladybug 😅 it was a friend of mine that introduced me to it and thanks to her I became a fan ❤️ And it’s fun to have someone to talk about a show and your crazy headcanons. I’m a sucker for romance so I ended up liking this show so much 😊

I was thinking about watching 101 Dalmatians Street too, I like the intro and I love dogs so I’ll give it a try and see how it goes 👍

Thanks for the ask and have a nice day!
